      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera S that presents in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish in its original Basalt Black Metallic paint, completely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium black leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the interior still retains that signature factory-fresh scent. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left Stuttgart. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, having been exclusively garage-kept and maintained with an open checkbook. It comes with a full, documented service history, two sets of keys, and the original owner\u2019s manuals. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
